BibliographicNote.Text: Dramma per musica in 3 acts; libretto by Nicola Francesco Haym, after Antonio Salvi and Pierre Corneille

Program notes by Andrew Jones, notes on the performing version by Alan Curtis, and synopsis by Donna Leon, all in English with German and French translations, and libretto in Italian with English, German, and French translations (150 p. : ports.) inserted in container
Recorded Sept. 2004, Sala Olimpia, Palazzo Doria Pamphilj, San Martino al Cimino, Italy and Nov. 2004, Friedrich-Ebert-Halle, Hamburg-Harburg
